PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779981070
OL,3,CMillions of Brits at risk of addiction
OL,4,Cto 'over the counter' medicines
OL,6,FThere are widespread concerns amongst
OL,7,Fmedical professionals about a hidden
OL,8,F'over the counter' dependency crisis
OL,9,Fin the UK - medicines that can form
OL,10,Fhabits but are available to purchase
OL,11,Fwithout a prescription, including
OL,12,Fpainkillers, sleeping aids and nasal
OL,13,Fsprays.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779981070
OL,3,CMillions of Brits at risk of addiction
OL,4,Cto 'over the counter' medicines
OL,6,FPainkillers containing a combination
OL,7,Fof codeine and either ibuprofen or
OL,8,Fparacetamol are available to buy at
OL,9,Fpharmacies without a prescription,
OL,10,Funlike more than 25 other countries
OL,11,Fincluding Australia, where the rules
OL,12,Fchanged in 2018 to reduce the risk of
OL,13,Fabuse and addiction.
OL,15,FThe current guidance on codeine-based
OL,16,Fpainkillers, which includes well-known
OL,17,Fbrands like Nurofen Plus and
OL,18,FSolpadeine, is that they should be
OL,19,Fused for a maximum of three days
OL,20,Fcontinuously.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
