OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779981070
OL,3,CMillions of Brits at risk of addiction
OL,4,Cto 'over the counter' medicines
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAccording to an ITV Tonight survey
OL,12,Fcarried out by Savanta of more than
OL,13,F2,000 people across the UK, almost one
OL,14,Fin five people who have taken codeine-
OL,15,Fbased painkillers did so for more than
OL,16,Ften days in a row, while one in six
OL,17,Ftook them for up to nine days.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779981070
OL,3,CMillions of Brits at risk of addiction
OL,4,Cto 'over the counter' medicines
OL,6,FAbby House says she developed an
OL,7,Faddiction after being prescribed
OL,8,Fcodeine following gastric sleeve
OL,9,Fsurgery and quickly turned to over the
OL,10,Fcounter painkillers to supplement her
OL,11,Fprescription.
OL,13,F"I was buying at least 20 boxes a
OL,14,Fweek, I'd say. I was taking so much
OL,15,Fthat it was making me sick," said the
OL,16,Fmother-of-two.
OL,18,F"There were 224 put on my repeat
OL,19,Fprescription. I would take those at my
OL,20,Fworst in about two to three days,"
OL,21,FAbby continued.
OL,26,@|D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779981070
OL,3,CMillions of Brits at risk of addiction
OL,4,Cto 'over the counter' medicines
OL,6,F"I went into #8,000 worth of debt and
OL,7,FI was using the money that I needed to
OL,8,Fpay my bills and my car insurance."
OL,10,FPainkillers with codeine are only
OL,11,Fallowed to be sold in the UK one pack
OL,12,Fat a time from a pharmacy.
OL,14,FPharmacists should remind the buyer
OL,15,Fthere is a three day guidance for use
OL,16,Fand if they believe that the medicine
OL,17,Fis being abused, they can refuse to
OL,18,Fsell them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779981070
OL,3,CMillions of Brits at risk of addiction
OL,4,Cto 'over the counter' medicines
OL,6,FBut for those with addictions like
OL,7,FAbby had, their solution is to simply
OL,8,F'pharmacy hop' - to drive around to
OL,9,Fdifferent pharmacies and buy a single
OL,10,Fpack at each. They have also reported
OL,11,Fon the ease of doing the same thing
OL,12,Fonline by visiting different
OL,13,Fpharmacies' websites.
OL,15,F"I believe (the ease of buying over
OL,16,Fthe counter painkillers) kept me in
OL,17,Faddiction for three years longer than
OL,18,FI needed to be," said the former NHS
OL,19,Femployee, who is now in recovery.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@LpmxD@XpnzD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779981070
OL,3,CMillions of Brits at risk of addiction
OL,4,Cto 'over the counter' medicines
OL,6,FAs well as causing dependencies, the
OL,7,Fprolonged overuse of codeine-
OL,8,Fcontaining painkillers can cause
OL,9,Fserious physical damage.
OL,11,FOther ingredients within them, such as
OL,12,Fparacetamol and ibuprofen can increase
OL,13,Fthe risk of problems including stomach
OL,14,Fulcers and perforation, as well as
OL,15,Fliver and kidney damage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779981070
OL,3,CMillions of Brits at risk of addiction
OL,4,Cto 'over the counter' medicines
OL,6,FPainkillers containing codeine aren't
OL,7,Fthe only over-the-counter medicines
OL,8,Ffueling dependency across the country.
OL,9,FFor the past year ITV News has
OL,10,Freported on decongestant nasal sprays
OL,11,Fcontaining either oxymetazoline or
OL,12,Fxylometazoline.
OL,14,FWhen used for more than seven days
OL,15,Fcontinuously, the sprays can cause a
OL,16,Fcondition called rebound congestion,
OL,17,Fwhere the nasal passages become
OL,18,Finflamed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779981070
OL,3,CMillions of Brits at risk of addiction
OL,4,Cto 'over the counter' medicines
OL,6,F"When I've tried to stop it before
OL,7,FI've just got really anxious. I just
OL,8,Ffeel like I can't breathe, I can't
OL,9,Feat, I can't sleep and it's
OL,10,Funcomfortable," says Georgia, who says
OL,11,Fshe has been dependent on decongestant
OL,12,Fsprays for two decades.
OL,14,FShe says it lead to a sensation of not
OL,15,Fbeing able to breathe and
OL,16,Fclaustrophobia, which was only
OL,17,Frelieved by using more of the spray.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779981070
OL,3,CMillions of Brits at risk of addiction
OL,4,Cto 'over the counter' medicines
OL,6,FAn ISPSOS survey commissioned last
OL,7,Fyear by ITV News suggested that up to
OL,8,F5.5 million people across the UK were
OL,9,Fpotentially exposing themselves to
OL,10,Fdependence by using nasal
OL,11,Fdecongestants containing either
OL,12,Fingredient for longer than the
OL,13,Fpreviously recommended seven days.
OL,15,FSince the potential scale of the issue
OL,16,Fwas highlighted in our reporting, the
OL,17,Fmedicines regulator, the MHRA, has
OL,18,Fchanged the guidance on the maximum
OL,19,Fusage period to five days.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779981070
OL,3,CMillions of Brits at risk of addiction
OL,4,Cto 'over the counter' medicines
OL,6,FIn a separate survey looking at sleep
OL,7,Faids containing H1 antihistamines, 1
OL,8,Fin 6 users of Nytol, 1 in 5 users of
OL,9,FSleepease and over a third of
OL,10,FPhenergen users admitted to using them
OL,11,Ffor longer than the recommended period.
OL,13,FH1 antihistamines are primarily a type
OL,14,Fof allergy medication with the side
OL,15,Feffect of causing drowsiness.
OL,16,FTolerance to the drowsy effects builds
OL,17,Fup quickly and can lead to strong
OL,18,Fhabit-forming psychological dependence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779981070
OL,3,CMillions of Brits at risk of addiction
OL,4,Cto 'over the counter' medicines
OL,6,F"They block a receptor in the brain
OL,7,Fand the body," says Dr Hugh Selsick,
OL,8,FConsultant in Psychiatry and Sleep
OL,9,FMedicine at UCLH.
OL,11,F"Long-term blockade of that receptor
OL,12,Fsignificantly increases the risk of
OL,13,Fcardiovascular disease and dementia."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779981070
OL,3,CMillions of Brits at risk of addiction
OL,4,Cto 'over the counter' medicines
OL,6,FITV Tonight spoke with a variety of
OL,7,Fexperts, who all shared concerns about
OL,8,Fa lack of data when it comes to the
OL,9,Fscale of dependency on common over the
OL,10,Fcounter medicines, which is why the
OL,11,Fthree surveys were commissioned. The
OL,12,Fseparate data that records supply and
OL,13,Fsales of these potentially habit
OL,14,Fforming medicines isn't joined up on
OL,15,Fany kind of accessible database.
OL,17,F"There is a challenge in that the data
OL,18,Fthat is available isn't joined up,"
OL,19,Fsays Dr Roz Gittins, Chief Pharmacy
OL,20,Fofficer of the General Pharmaceutical
OL,21,FCouncil.
OL,26,@yD@AOUzD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779981070
OL,3,CMillions of Brits at risk of addiction
OL,4,Cto 'over the counter' medicines
OL,6,F"As the regulator of pharmacies, we
OL,7,Fdon't have sight of that data, we
OL,8,Fdon't have access to that information."
OL,10,FIt makes any kind of plan to combat
OL,11,Fthe hidden crisis far more difficult,
OL,12,Fas the government doesn't know how
OL,13,Fmany people are affected, where any
OL,14,Fhotspots may be or whether current
OL,15,Fguidelines are suitable.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
